          "_name": "features7",
          "_sourceTheme": "mobirise5",
          "_customHTML": "<section data-bs-version=\"5.1\" class=\"features7\" group=\"Features\" data-bg-video=\"{{bg.type == 'video' && bg.value.url}}\" mbr-class=\"{'mbr-parallax-background': bg.parallax}\">\n    <!---->\n    <mbr-parameters>\n        <header>Size</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Full Width\" name=\"fullWidth\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Reverse\" name=\"reverseContent\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Top\" name=\"paddingTop\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"5\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Bottom\" name=\"paddingBottom\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"5\">\n        <input type=\"range\" name=\"imageWidth\" title=\"Image\" min=\"4\" max=\"8\" step=\"1\" value=\"6\">\n        <header>Show/Hide</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Title\" name=\"showTitle\" checked>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Text\" name=\"showText\" checked>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Cost\" name=\"showCost\" checked>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Buttons\" name=\"showButtons\" checked>\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Color\" name=\"cardsBg\" value=\"#e6c63b\">\n        <header>Background</header>\n        <fieldset type=\"background\" name=\"bg\" parallax>\n            <input type=\"image\" title=\"Image\" value=\"../_images/background1.jpg\" parallax>\n            <input type=\"color\" title=\"Color\" value=\"#232323\" selected>\n            <input type=\"video\" title=\"Video\" value=\"https://vimeo.com/428046504\">\n        </fieldset>\n        <header condition=\"bg.type === 'video'\">Fallback Image</header>\n        <input type=\"image\" title=\"Fallback Image\" value=\"../_images/background13.jpg\" name=\"fallBackImage\" condition=\"bg.type === 'video'\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Overlay\" name=\"overlay\" checked condition=\"bg.type !== 'color'\">\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Overlay Color\" name=\"overlayColor\" value=\"#bed3f9\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Opacity\" name=\"overlayOpacity\" min=\"0\" max=\"1\" step=\"0.1\" value=\"0.5\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n    </mbr-parameters>\n\n    <div class=\"mbr-fallback-image disabled\" mbr-if=\"bg.type == 'video'\"></div>\n    <div class=\"mbr-overlay\" mbr-if=\"overlay && bg.type!== 'color'\" mbr-style=\"{'opacity': overlayOpacity, 'background-color': overlayColor}\">\n    </div>\n    <div mbr-class=\"{'container': !fullWidth, 'container-fluid' : fullWidth}\">\n        <div class=\"card-wrapper\">\n            <div class=\"row align-items-center\" mbr-class=\"{'flex-row-reverse' : reverseContent}\">\n                <div class=\"col-12 col-lg-{{imageWidth}}\">\n                    <div class=\"image-wrapper\">\n                        <img src=\"@PROJECT_PATH@/assets/images/493897557-9767771803304896-5978253786903355855-n-1256x942.jpg\" alt=\"Mobirise Website Builder\">\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"col-12 col-lg\">\n                    <div class=\"text-box\">\n                        <h5 class=\"mbr-title mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-2\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-title\">\n                            <b>Special Offer</b>\n                        </h5>\n                        <p class=\"mbr-text mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showText\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text, .cost, .mbr-section-btn\"><br>If you're looking to lighten your workload, I’m here to help make things easier and more efficient. I can streamline tasks and ensure faster, smoother transactions. Consider this a special offer to save you time while maintaining quality and reliability.<br><br></p>\n                        <div class=\"cost\" mbr-if=\"showCost\">\n                            <span mbr-text mbr-theme-style=\"display-1\" class=\"currentcost mbr-fonts-style pr-2\" data-app-selector=\".currentcost\">$15</span>\n                            <span mbr-text mbr-theme-style=\"display-1\" class=\"oldcost mbr-fonts-style\" data-app-selector=\".oldcost\">$29</span>\n                        </div>\n                        <div mbr-buttons mbr-theme-style=\"display-4\" class=\"mbr-section-btn pt-3\" mbr-if=\"showButtons\" data-toolbar=\"-mbrBtnMove\"><a href=\"index.html#schedule\" class=\"btn btn-danger\" data-app-placeholder=\"Type Text\">Schedule a Meeting Now!</a></div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</section>",
